verbose_text: By performing a pairwise comparison between the earliest time points of the FBS and A2S time course (cluster 3 versus cluster 5; XREF_FIG), we found that FBS cells on day 3 still retained the expression of genes associated with system development (Col3a1) as well as signal transduction (Fgf7, Egr1, and Igfbp3) that were greatly reduced by day 2 of A2S reprogramming.
